{"tid":986384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡空軍主力戰機升級 將對美採購F-35匿蹤戰機","createTime":"2019-01-18T11:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T00:21:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"01a708fa2ce8c026496115e3097e37f66973dd74","tid":986384,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2019/01/18/94ff1b72cabe37168b0252b977b902bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2019%2F01%2F18%2F94ff1b72cabe37168b0252b977b902bc.jpg&h=c75e9132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-35<br />\n <br />\n新加坡國防<br />\n時間：2019-01-18 17:28新聞引據：採訪、路透社撰稿編輯：李協芳<br />\n<br />\n美國洛克希德馬丁公司出產的F-35A戰機。(圖：維基百科)<br />\n新加坡國防部長今天(18日)表示，洛克希德&middot;馬丁公司(Lockheed Martin)的F-35戰機將是汰換該國現有F-16戰機中隊的最適合選擇。星國已計畫先採購「幾架」進行評估。<br />\n<br />\n擁有東南亞最多國防預算的新加坡，對全球軍火公司來說是個極力想爭取的機會。星國目前正準備投資新技術及升級設備。<br />\n<br />\n星國空軍60架左右的F-16戰機，自1998年開始服役，預計將於2030年後除役。<br />\n<br />\n國防部長黃永宏(Ng Eng Hen)在臉書(Facebook)上提到，「他們(國防部)已決定，F-35戰機會是最適合的汰換機型。」<br />\n<br />\n他補充說，「我們想先採購幾架，以在決定購買一整個中隊前，對F-35性能進行全面的評估。」<br />\n<br />\n黃永宏表示，星國國防部會與美國方面進行進一步的接洽，但完成首筆交易合約需要9至12個月的時間。<br />\n<br />\nF-35戰機是世界上最先進的戰鬥機之一，佔洛克希德總營收的25%。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國五角大廈的合約協商，以最為普遍的F-35A型來說，每架價格約為9千萬美元(約新台幣27.9億元)。<br />\n<br />\nF-35的價格一直飽受美國總統川普(Donald Trump)與其他官員的批評，他們也曾指出F-35許多生產延遲和成本超支的問題。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月28日一架F-35B型戰機在南卡羅來納州波弗特(Beaufort)附近墜毀後，洛克希德&middot;馬丁停飛了所有F-35戰機，並對發動機進行檢修。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2008720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2008720&d=xP31a004xBweYVfCBK2M7ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=535c6d28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2008720</a>"},{"pid":"c4ab318782801f7510ab5cfa3e23efaddfd3fa9f","tid":986384,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"幾時到香港國空軍有f35<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[black]之後比班小學雞炒爛曬[/black]</span>"},{"pid":"2c468fb62236d06f8aae3c5dba5a952e541e80bd","tid":986384,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"F15SE?"},{"pid":"d28cc5ca9efdf5e1c9f994e735ecddd84a1db6ce","tid":986384,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"F35已經解決左生產同價錢問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71680fb95aa7a57cabad4301262f1d1600a834a8","tid":986384,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c468fb62236d06f8aae3c5dba5a952e541e80bd","tid":986384,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"F15SE?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"咪有F-15SG囉"},{"pid":"8fe78165761f14bad8674a4611ac661ee8cd0ce9","tid":986384,"uid":24903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"香港儲備買倒幾多架F35A?"},{"pid":"c9b6b4b98cd38ec53bd0916c66fb52abb09c8d7d","tid":986384,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8fe78165761f14bad8674a4611ac661ee8cd0ce9","tid":986384,"uid":24903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"香港儲備買倒幾多架F35A?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"唔計儲備，剩係沙中線重建紅磡站月台嘅洗費，都夠買10架8架F35  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586f3a9c96d2e0382eac25b78e8696e18bdec6cc","tid":986384,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d28cc5ca9efdf5e1c9f994e735ecddd84a1db6ce","tid":986384,"uid":121146,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"F35已經解決左生產同價錢問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src